For every second:
    1. Read game world data (DB).

    2. for player in players:
        2.1. Update context.
        2.2. Run users code in isolatred VM.

    3. Update game world data (DB).
    4. Store result (snapshot) to the queue (optional?).
    5. Send update to all connected clients.

------------------------------------------------------------

Add player script execution to queue (use some message broker)?
